---
title: Chinese Beef & Ginger Noodles with Crushed Peanuts
description: It's easy to whip up a tasty stir-fry sauce with our tried-and-true formula including fresh ginger, nutty sesame seeds and a touch of honey. Use it in this colourful veggie and beef stir-fry that will have the whole family satisfied!
